### Pipeline Steps

0. Update transcript to automatically start/restart the pipeline below
1. Use ChatGPT o3 API to generate a comprehensive summary of transcript and Keywords.
2. Use X API to gather tweets based on the o3 generated keywords.
3. Use gemini-cli (local/free) to generate "few shot" examples of relevant/unrelevant tweets.
4. Use gemma-3n (local/free) with the "few shot" examples + summary to determine if a tweet is relevant
5. Send relevant tweets to deepseek-r1 (local/free) which is trained on summary
6. Optionally send to ChatGPT 4.1-nano API for tweet polish + condensing to correct character count
7. Tweets to queue for manual approval/editing.
8. Approved tweets are published as a comment using X API